{"tid":2448653,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"立場：中國疑封鎖即時通訊軟件 Signal","createTime":"2021-03-16T05:24:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-16T06:40:49.000Z","uid":22556,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"26cd4c06439529c6b9ac2d1a7e35f9da596f63ba","tid":2448653,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T05:24:41.000Z","msg":"科技媒體 TechCrunch 發現，中國用戶在今日（16 日）起無法再使用即時通訊軟件 Signal ，專門追蹤網站審查的 <a href=\"http://Greatfire.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGreatfire.org&d=HziU8jWK8j2Oa3ZLfTDirJhbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=83279426\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Greatfire.org</a> 亦發現在再前一日 (15/3) 已無法在中國境內瀏覽 Signal 的官方網站。<br />\n<br />\nSignal 原本是少數在中國境內，無需使用虛擬私人網絡 (VPN) 可使用的即時通訊軟件。該通訊軟件以其加密性、高私隱度聞名，廣為傳媒、社運人士，以至一般民眾使用。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/technology/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%96%91%E5%B0%81%E9%8E%96%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E9%80%9A%E8%A8%8A%E8%BB%9F%E4%BB%B6-signal/?fbclid=IwAR1VZuTkvNDbK8oNuJHH0gPoox_NbUspIeVI6XMzHyDjQSyZlAvm2sdcGQo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Ftechnology%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%2596%2591%25E5%25B0%2581%25E9%258E%2596%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E9%2580%259A%25E8%25A8%258A%25E8%25BB%259F%25E4%25BB%25B6-signal%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1VZuTkvNDbK8oNuJHH0gPoox_NbUspIeVI6XMzHyDjQSyZlAvm2sdcGQo&d=HziU8jWK8j2Oa3ZLfTDirJhbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=70cdd8a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Ftechnology%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%2596%2591%25E5%25B0%2581%25E9%258E%2596%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E9%2580%259A%25E8%25A8%258A%25E8%25BB%259F%25E4%25BB%25B6-signal%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1VZuTkvNDbK8oNuJHH0gPoox_NbUspIeVI6XMzHyDjQSyZlAvm2sdcGQo&h=86b76921\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/technology/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%96%91%E5%B0%81%E9%8E%96%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E9%80%9A%E8%A8%8A%E8%BB%9F%E4%BB%B6-signal/?fbclid=IwAR